472
00:29:37,799 --> 00:29:39,354
Kudo?

473
00:29:40,169 --> 00:29:43,594
Apakah begitu?

474
00:29:43,594 --> 00:29:46,220
Apakah dia benar-benar menimbulkan kebencian sebesar itu?

475
00:29:46,220 --> 00:29:49,330
Ya, pusaran kebencian sedang berkecamuk.

476
00:29:49,330 --> 00:29:53,670
Dia melakukan persis seperti yang saya harapkan.

477
00:30:04,426 --> 00:30:05,978
Hai!

478
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:13,985
Kudo.

479
00:30:13,985 --> 00:30:16,098
Di Sini.

480
00:30:16,098 --> 00:30:18,733
Tangkap dengan benar lain kali.

481
00:30:19,399 --> 00:30:20,858
Hai!

482
00:30:24,378 --> 00:30:28,208
Mimpi adalah rumahku.

483
00:30:29,447 --> 00:30:33,349
Aku telah mendedikasikan 11 tahun hidupku
